<i>noun</i>: 헌신 [헌ː신], 투신 [투신], 충실 [충실], 집중 [집쭝], 지성 [지성], 정진 [정진], 전념 [전념], 신앙심 [시ː낭심] <br>
<ul>
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>헌신 [헌ː신]</dt><br>
<dd>devotion; dedication; commitment</dd><br>
<dd>몸과 마음을 바쳐 모든 정성과 노력을 다함.</dd><br>
<dd>An act of trying hard sincerely to do something with one's heart and soul.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>투신 [투신]</dt><br>
<dd>1. devotion; dedication</dd><br>
<dd>어떤 일이나 직업, 분야 등에 온갖 정열을 다해 마음을 쏟음.</dd><br>
<dd>The state of passionately making all-out efforts in a certain task, job, field, etc.</dd><br>
<dd>2. death-leap</dd><br>
<dd>죽기 위해 높은 곳에서 아래로 몸을 던짐.</dd><br>
<dd>An act of jumping from a high place to commit suicide.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>충실 [충실]</dt><br>
<dd>faithfulness; devotion; sincerity</dd><br>
<dd>충성스럽고 정직하며 성실함.</dd><br>
<dd>The state of being loyal, honest, and sincere.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>집중 [집쭝]</dt><br>
<dd>1. concentration</dd><br>
<dd>한곳을 중심으로 하여 모임. 또는 그렇게 모음.</dd><br>
<dd>An act of gathering in a place, or an act of gathering things or people in a place.</dd><br>
<dd>2. concentration; devotion</dd><br>
<dd>한 가지 일에 모든 힘을 쏟아부음.</dd><br>
<dd>An act of putting all one's energy into one thing.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>지성 [지성]</dt><br>
<dd>devotion; dedication</dd><br>
<dd>지극한 정성.</dd><br>
<dd>Heartfelt devotion</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>정진 [정진]</dt><br>
<dd>1. devotion</dd><br>
<dd>힘쓰고 노력하여 나아감.</dd><br>
<dd>The act of progressing by working hard and making efforts.</dd><br>
<dd>2. devotion</dd><br>
<dd>몸을 깨끗이 하고 마음을 가다듬음.</dd><br>
<dd>The act of keeping one's body clean and mind poised.</dd><br>
<dd>3. devotion</dd><br>
<dd>불교에서, 항상 불도를 닦아 게을리하지 않음.</dd><br>
<dd>In Buddhism, the state of refraining from indolence and always practicing the teachings of the Buddha.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>전념 [전념]</dt><br>
<dd>devotion</dd><br>
<dd>오직 한 가지 일에만 마음을 씀.</dd><br>
<dd>The act of concentrating one's mind on one thing only.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>신앙심 [시ː낭심]</dt><br>
<dd>piety; devotion</dd><br>
<dd>신을 믿고 따르며 받드는 마음.</dd><br>
<dd>Devotion and reverence to a god.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>